WEBVTT

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:42.079
Brother Long

00:00:42.719 --> 00:00:44.200
Zhu Yihai's men are in the club

00:00:44.719 --> 00:00:45.640
I caught her

00:00:47.920 --> 00:00:49.119
Without me

00:00:50.200 --> 00:00:52.759
you'd still be a bargirl

00:00:53.359 --> 00:00:54.479
I'll kill you!

00:00:54.920 --> 00:00:55.600
Jiao Jing

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:02.479
Jiao Jing!

00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:06.079
Qian Huilian's

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:08.920
in the suitcase

00:01:11.799 --> 00:01:12.640
Son of a bitch!

00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:15.000
Don't let him get away!

00:01:31.159 --> 00:01:32.280
Brother Fan

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:12.159
I've already called the cops.

00:02:13.319 --> 00:02:14.400
Don't even think about running.

00:02:18.759 --> 00:02:19.879
You? Stop me?

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:22.599
Don't think all your dirty deeds

00:02:23.199 --> 00:02:24.800
will let you escape the law.

00:02:25.360 --> 00:02:27.000
This time, you're not getting away.

00:02:27.960 --> 00:02:29.639
The old man said it before.

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:31.080
Someone like you,

00:02:31.960 --> 00:02:33.400
you don't deserve any kindness.

00:02:33.840 --> 00:02:34.400
What?

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:37.879
You think you're qualified to lecture me?

00:02:39.479 --> 00:02:41.080
Watch me prove I am.

00:03:10.159 --> 00:03:12.400
This punch is for Sun Qian.

00:03:22.719 --> 00:03:24.080
And this one,

00:03:24.080 --> 00:03:26.319
that's for kidnapping Huilian!

00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:41.759
This one's

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:43.199
for Jiao Jing.

00:03:43.879 --> 00:03:44.840
For Dali.

00:03:45.159 --> 00:03:46.120
For Ge Bing.

00:03:46.120 --> 00:03:46.879
For Wei Wei.

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:47.840
Director Ge,

00:03:47.879 --> 00:03:49.879
this is for treating lives like dirt!

00:03:56.400 --> 00:03:58.000
Who else?

00:03:59.560 --> 00:04:01.400
And this one's for my dad!

00:04:01.400 --> 00:04:03.439
I don't even know your dad!

00:04:18.199 --> 00:04:19.079
Mom!

00:04:21.759 --> 00:04:23.279
I'm here to save you!

00:04:25.279 --> 00:04:26.439
Zhu Yihai!

00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:29.240
You ruined everything!

00:04:30.199 --> 00:04:31.800
I'll kill you!

00:04:36.959 --> 00:04:37.600
What are you doing here?

00:04:37.600 --> 00:04:38.959
Your eye's fine, huh?

00:04:50.839 --> 00:04:51.879
Long Xiao!

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:53.639
Don't play dead with me.

00:04:53.639 --> 00:04:54.160
Get the hell up!

00:04:54.399 --> 00:04:55.399
Where's Huilian?

00:04:55.560 --> 00:04:57.399
Talk! Where's Qian Huilian?

00:05:03.560 --> 00:05:04.399
Zhu Yihai!

00:05:05.000 --> 00:05:05.879
If you beat him to death,

00:05:06.199 --> 00:05:07.839
none of us will ever find Huilian.

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:11.600
You guys go look for her. Hurry!

00:05:11.720 --> 00:05:12.160
Right.

00:05:12.959 --> 00:05:13.680
Let's go!

00:05:15.319 --> 00:05:16.120
Long Xiao,

00:05:16.600 --> 00:05:17.879
just tell me,

00:05:17.879 --> 00:05:19.199
where did you hide Qian Huilian?

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:20.920
I'm begging you, okay?

00:05:25.720 --> 00:05:26.720
By five o'clock,

00:05:28.560 --> 00:05:30.199
Qian Huilian will be dead!

00:05:35.560 --> 00:05:36.319
Sun Qian.

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:38.680
Did you see Qian Huilian?

00:05:42.199 --> 00:05:43.000
Any luck? Did you find her?

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:44.759
Zhu Yihai, I'm telling you,

00:05:45.319 --> 00:05:46.600
if we can't find Huilian,

00:05:46.600 --> 00:05:47.600
I'll kill you!

00:05:47.920 --> 00:05:48.639
Kill me?

00:05:48.720 --> 00:05:50.040
I'm more worried than you are!

00:05:50.040 --> 00:05:51.000
All right, enough.

00:05:51.279 --> 00:05:52.720
Forget about that for now.

00:05:52.720 --> 00:05:54.040
Go find Huilian first.

00:05:54.120 --> 00:05:55.199
Once the cops show up,

00:05:55.199 --> 00:05:56.079
we'll be in trouble.

00:05:56.560 --> 00:05:57.800
Leave this to us.

00:05:58.319 --> 00:05:59.399
Go, now!

00:06:05.279 --> 00:06:06.040
Officer!

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:07.399
Officer!

00:06:07.759 --> 00:06:08.720
Listen to me.

00:06:08.720 --> 00:06:09.720
Brother Hai, Brother Hai is a good guy.

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:10.480
He helped us out.

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:11.079
We're the good guys.

00:06:11.079 --> 00:06:11.920
You've gotta believe us.

00:06:19.560 --> 00:06:20.560
Yihai, you're here.

00:06:20.800 --> 00:06:21.600
How'd it go?

00:06:21.920 --> 00:06:23.560
Long Xiao's been caught,

00:06:24.079 --> 00:06:25.839
but where Long Xiao hid Qian Huilian,

00:06:26.480 --> 00:06:27.920
I have no idea.

00:06:28.839 --> 00:06:29.800
Dad.

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:31.360
Dahai,

00:06:31.360 --> 00:06:32.600
you're one of our own.

00:06:32.600 --> 00:06:34.040
I'll definitely help.

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:39.720
Attention, all factory workers!

00:06:40.319 --> 00:06:42.759
Our worker Qian Huilian is missing.

00:06:43.720 --> 00:06:45.720
All workers, drop what you're doing

00:06:45.839 --> 00:06:47.240
and search for Qian Huilian.

00:06:47.480 --> 00:06:50.560
Find her and get the Model Worker title.

00:06:51.120 --> 00:06:52.120
That's perfect.

00:06:53.480 --> 00:06:54.360
My chance has come.

00:06:56.160 --> 00:06:57.199
Times create heroes.

00:07:05.040 --> 00:07:05.839
Huilian!

00:07:06.319 --> 00:07:07.120
Huilian!

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:09.600
Huilian!

00:07:18.079 --> 00:07:19.639
Wait, this isn't right.

00:07:20.839 --> 00:07:23.319
Long Xiao wouldn't hide her at his place.

00:07:28.040 --> 00:07:28.839
Mom,

00:07:30.399 --> 00:07:32.279
where on earth are you?

00:07:42.920 --> 00:07:44.319
My dad did this, didn't he?

00:07:45.240 --> 00:07:46.040
Old bastard.

00:07:47.680 --> 00:07:48.639
You're really lucky.

00:07:49.519 --> 00:07:50.279
Don't worry.

00:07:51.639 --> 00:07:53.199
I'll definitely get her back for you.

00:07:53.720 --> 00:07:54.199
Here's the plan.

00:07:54.639 --> 00:07:56.120
I'll go give a statement to the police.

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:57.399
Let's split up and search.

00:07:57.600 --> 00:07:58.040
Sound good?

00:07:58.959 --> 00:07:59.519
Let's go.

00:08:00.240 --> 00:08:00.879
Stop dawdling, everyone.

00:08:00.879 --> 00:08:01.680
Hurry up and search.

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:03.160
Hey, hey, wait.

00:08:03.439 --> 00:08:04.879
I think I just remembered something.

00:08:05.879 --> 00:08:06.839
What did you remember?

00:08:07.360 --> 00:08:08.120
Where's Brother Hai?

00:08:08.399 --> 00:08:09.600
Let's hurry and find Brother Hai.

00:08:09.639 --> 00:08:10.000
Go, go, go.

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:11.160
Move.

00:08:14.519 --> 00:08:15.000
Lili.

00:08:15.720 --> 00:08:17.160
You've gotta help me.

00:08:19.399 --> 00:08:20.439
Help you find Qian Huilian?

00:08:21.040 --> 00:08:21.680
Right.

00:08:21.959 --> 00:08:23.079
You're the only one who can.

00:08:25.040 --> 00:08:26.560
Is she really that important to you?

00:08:26.639 --> 00:08:28.160
Of course she's important.

00:08:34.639 --> 00:08:36.200
But she's been gone so long now.

00:08:36.200 --> 00:08:37.200
Where are you gonna find her?

00:08:39.279 --> 00:08:40.200
I've got it.

00:08:40.360 --> 00:08:40.879
Let's go.

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:52.919
Why do you think she'd be here?

00:08:54.399 --> 00:08:56.080
Ge Bing was tied up here before.

00:08:56.399 --> 00:08:57.919
Long Xiao isn't from our factory.

00:08:58.120 --> 00:08:59.200
He doesn't know that many places.

00:08:59.360 --> 00:09:00.799
Then maybe she's not at the factory.

00:09:00.799 --> 00:09:01.320
No, Lili.

00:09:01.320 --> 00:09:02.159
Let me ask you this.

00:09:02.639 --> 00:09:04.440
If you didn't want me to see Huilian,

00:09:04.440 --> 00:09:05.360
what would you do?

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:08.440
I'd kill her right in front of you.

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:10.000
Exactly.

00:09:10.519 --> 00:09:12.240
Long Xiao would use the cruelest way

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:14.000
to kill Qian Huilian in front of me.

00:09:14.919 --> 00:09:16.120
She must be at the factory.

00:09:17.320 --> 00:09:18.039
Brother Hai.

00:09:18.519 --> 00:09:18.960
Dahai.

00:09:19.000 --> 00:09:19.759
What is it, Dali?

00:09:19.759 --> 00:09:20.240
Did you find her?

00:09:20.399 --> 00:09:20.919
No.

00:09:21.039 --> 00:09:22.080
She's anxious to find you.

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:23.519
I think I saw Long Xiao

00:09:23.679 --> 00:09:25.919
dragging a suitcase out of the karaoke.

00:09:26.399 --> 00:09:27.200
And then?

00:09:27.960 --> 00:09:29.120
There is no "and then."

00:09:29.360 --> 00:09:30.519
Isn't that useless?

00:09:30.519 --> 00:09:31.320
Wait a minute.

00:09:31.480 --> 00:09:34.519
If Long Xiao put Huilian in the suitcase,

00:09:34.799 --> 00:09:37.399
he wouldn't run around town with it.

00:09:39.159 --> 00:09:40.399
There's a clue in Long Xiao's car.

00:09:40.639 --> 00:09:41.159
Let's go.

00:09:43.840 --> 00:09:45.080
Hurry, Long Xiao's car.

00:09:45.480 --> 00:09:46.399
There's probably a clue.

00:09:57.519 --> 00:09:58.320
What's wrong, Wei Wei?

00:09:58.960 --> 00:10:00.000
It's nothing, nothing.

00:10:00.799 --> 00:10:01.919
I just need a moment.

00:10:02.039 --> 00:10:02.799
If it's too much, go to the hospital.

00:10:02.799 --> 00:10:03.360
Don't push yourself.

00:10:03.360 --> 00:10:03.879
No way.

00:10:03.879 --> 00:10:04.360
Just go.

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:06.559
Right now Huilian matters more than me.

00:10:11.320 --> 00:10:12.279
Bro, I found something.

00:10:13.320 --> 00:10:14.120
What did you find?

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:16.440
That sulfur smell, no doubt about it.

00:10:17.399 --> 00:10:18.200
What does that mean?

00:10:18.200 --> 00:10:19.080
This is blast furnace slag.

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:20.639
Forgot our factory used to make this?

00:10:21.000 --> 00:10:22.399
We used to, but not anymore.

00:10:22.399 --> 00:10:23.759
The formula was changed long ago.

00:10:24.399 --> 00:10:25.639
We don't make this anymore.

00:10:26.799 --> 00:10:27.919
I get it now.

00:10:28.519 --> 00:10:30.519
Back when our factory shipped goods,

00:10:30.639 --> 00:10:32.080
they always went through the old station.

00:10:32.519 --> 00:10:34.360
Back then, this stuff was everywhere.

00:10:35.679 --> 00:10:36.000
Let's go.

00:10:36.440 --> 00:10:37.159
To the station.